{"tid":1332474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再開d疑似分化嘅Post","createTime":"2019-07-19T10:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T10:34:15.000Z","uid":67229,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b79bffb42e6f0b23382db28b1c46b4c10149f8b3","tid":1332474,"uid":67229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T10:12:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再開任何同推任何疑似分化嘅Post啦 專心返係721</span></span><br />\n<br />\n政府總部內部不尋常嚴密部署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1332190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1332190</a><br />\n<br />\n好似依個post咁 我都想肯定樓主唔係有心分化<br />\n但係依個時間講話政府有部署 其實只係叫職員收好d野 又唔知佢真正嘅目的係咩<br />\n如果真係有義士721入左政總咪一定會比人話係鬼 係咪會令到真係想衝嘅義士唔膽衝<br />\n咪姐係同上次衝立法會警犬擺空城計令到人以為衝嘅義士係鬼一樣<br />\n<br />\n我明好多手足做咁多野都係想為件事想好 <br />\n但係有時真係會唔小心做左分化撚<br />\n專注返係721好過啦"},{"pid":"870f62e096b4b34bde138edf0accc04edfe6f454","tid":1332474,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T10:12:35.000Z","msg":"【有人冒警】面對冒警情境練習場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1332100\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1332100</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警\n你扮警察\n冇委任證\n涉嫌傷人\n藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"40f2e019a51cd8f06bfbb103f323522b97ce875b","tid":1332474,"uid":67229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T10:15:03.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"f065ee36389bd3888c3e95ccc1b900d122cd1461","tid":1332474,"uid":67229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T10:15:34.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"f3a3fd0ec51c99e3ed3c79920e10308adfcbebf1","tid":1332474,"uid":67229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T10:16:03.000Z","msg":"推到上熱門"},{"pid":"2bd363bbec54d2cd4722676c2e4a5483ee7b2b9e","tid":1332474,"uid":67229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T10:17:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4cfde580e8a57ad5bfc82ff5339b4bf7eba64b7","tid":1332474,"uid":67229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco